---
title: Rice Pilaf
---

== Cooking Rice with Vermicelli ==

Melt butter in #skillet{}.

Add @salt{1%tablespoon}.

Brown @vermicelli noodles{3-4%ounces} in butter and salt.

Add @Uncle Ben's Converted Rice{3%cups} and brown that as well.

Add @Chicken Broth{6%cups} and cover with #lid{}.

Turn heat to low for ~{35%minutes}.